headline: Q3 2025 Insurance Labor Market Study Results Reflect Employment Growth

headline: NFP Appoints Tom Ryan to Lead Complex Risk Business in Central and West Regions
summary: NFP, an Aon company and leading property and casualty (P&C) broker, benefits consultant, wealth manager and retirement plan advisor, has appointed Tom Ryan as managing director of Complex Risk for its Central and West regions. Based in the Chicago area, Ryan will report to Sean Hickey, senior vice president of Complex Risk, and work closely with Amanda Ruback and Brian Bonnell, managing directors ofP&C for NFP's Central and West regions, respectively.
